Lee Anne Wong, "Dumplings All Day Wong: A Cookbook of Asian Delights From a Top Chef"
ISBN: 1624140599 | 2014 | EPUB | 256 pages | 48 MB

Making tasty, unique dumplings has never been easier with celebrity chef, Lee Anne Wong's most coveted recipes and techniques. Each recipe will have you creating one-of-a-kind dumplings and noodles to wow your family and friends.

Lee Anne Wong was one of the top four contestants on Bravo's Top Chef as well as a judge on Chopped and a guest on Unique Eats, The Wendy Williams Show, Iron Chef America and Unwrapped.

With delicious recipes such as Pork and Chive Dumplings with Soy Ginger Sauce, Sweet Corn Tamale Dumplings with Sesame-Avocado Sauce and Chicken Pad Thai Wontons with Spicy Peanut Sauce, you'll have all your guests begging for more. You'll be a Dumpling Master in no time!
